Aku punya ide.

507
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:04,800
Michael.

508
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:05,680
Cium.

509
00:29:09,690 --> 00:29:10,650
Qiyi.

510
00:29:12,630 --> 00:29:13,360
Di sana ada tidak?

511
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,100
Tidak ada.

512
00:29:36,400 --> 00:29:38,930
Kenapa... kau mau datang ke sini?

513
00:29:41,770 --> 00:29:43,840
